
background layers:

* selectable in Top Pane
* draggable in Top Pane on the Z axis
* size determined from mosaic tiles
* drawn using the X ranges of the mosaic tiles

state loading:

* background auto loads layer positions from bgLayers.json file
* push to server button 

Enemy Model:

* single position
* selectable in Live and Top panes
* draggable in Live and Top panes
